         Why should thier be an incentive to use other pets?  We don't use our previous pets up to level 53.  Would you use a 44 pet instead of your 49 pet?  The higher the pet level, the better it should be, PERIOD.  The spectre should be the ultimate pet, cause its so hard to get to 59, get the spell, cost is high etc.. </P><P> We aren't mages and we shouldn't have situational pets.  The monk pet is nice, but do you think we should have a pet at 56 that does more damage then the one we get at 59?  We fight mobs that hit MUCH harder at 60 then we do at 56.  The only pet that should be able to outdamage the spectre is the 53 pet when it gets to backstab full time.  The rogue pet has low hps and defense, so its higher situational damage is ok.</P><P>Just figure out what the hell is wrong with the specs offensive(dual wield) ability and fix it.</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
